349
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:44,580
 u evanđelje,

350
00:26:44,580 --> 00:26:45,420
 to su progonstva,

351
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:46,200
 to je svječnjak,

352
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,280
 to je,

353
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:49,620
 strpinac je to imao,

354
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:49,840
 ono,

355
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:51,740
 zasijavio je pred cijeli svijetom,

356
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:53,440
 možda ja i ti nećemo imati tu priliku,

357
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,600
 možda ćemo biti mučenici,

358
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:54,940
 ne znam,

359
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:56,180
 to je jako lako

360
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,000
 današnje Evropi,

361
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,140
 u Srepariza su nedavno

362
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:01,260
 zaklali svećenika na misi,

363
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:02,340
 došo je islamista,

364
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:03,300
 ja vam zaklali svećenika

365
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:05,160
 na sredmisenog starog svećenika,

366
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:07,000
 vrlo lako da ćemo biti,

367
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:07,640
 i mučenici,

368
00:27:07,640 --> 00:27:09,620
 ako nam Bog da tu milost,

369
00:27:09,620 --> 00:27:10,160
 taj dar,

370
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:11,500
 Bog daje ih snagu,

371
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,640
 zato kad dođe do toga,

372
00:27:12,640 --> 00:27:14,480
 onima koji su njegovi,

373
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:14,980
 naravno,

374
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:15,780
 evo,

375
00:27:15,780 --> 00:27:16,620
 evo,

376
00:27:16,620 --> 00:27:20,120
 idemo na bit ovoga,

377
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:21,400
 što je ovaj svječnjak,

378
00:27:21,400 --> 00:27:22,400
 što je ova,

379
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,720
 gdje se vidi ova sol,

380
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,140
 to je u trenucima,

381
00:27:25,140 --> 00:27:27,400
 kada neko ide protiv nas,

382
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,140
 kada govori protiv nas,

383
00:27:29,140 --> 00:27:30,500
 kada nas je oklevetalo,

384
00:27:30,500 --> 00:27:32,660
 kada nam stavlja nogu na postu,

385
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:33,620
 ne da nam da napredujemo,

386
00:27:33,620 --> 00:27:34,480
 izmisli bilo šta,

387
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:37,060
 gdje vidiš da neko ide protiv tvojeg života,

388
00:27:37,060 --> 00:27:39,020
 ako imaš samo ovaj život,

389
00:27:39,020 --> 00:27:39,700
