411
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:10,000
 kad se događa svječnjak,

412
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,680
 onaj koji,

413
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:12,680
 kaže,

414
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,940
 onaj koji nema,

415
00:28:13,940 --> 00:28:15,460
 ne kaže,

416
00:28:15,460 --> 00:28:16,280
 onaj koji ima,

417
00:28:16,280 --> 00:28:17,700
 nadodaće mu se,

418
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:19,460
 a onaj koji nema,

419
00:28:19,460 --> 00:28:20,600
 oduzeće mu se

420
00:28:20,600 --> 00:28:22,060
 i ono što misli da ima.

421
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:24,060
 To je,

422
00:28:24,060 --> 00:28:24,880
 kad dođe svječnjak,

423
00:28:24,880 --> 00:28:26,500
 kad se dogodi jedna ovakva situacija,

424
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:28,840
 a događa će ti se,

425
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,840
 u manjoj ili u većoj mjeri,

426
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,260
 tada,

427
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:33,400
 i ti misliš,

428
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,040
 ja sam katolik,

429
00:28:34,040 --> 00:28:34,640
 ja sam kršan,

430
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,400
 ja sam svječnjak,

431
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,720
 ja idem na misu i tako dalje,

432
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,340
 tada,

433
00:28:38,340 --> 00:28:39,240
 ako nemaš,

434
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,680
 stvarno,

435
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:41,300
 ako nemaš,

436
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:42,860
 oduzeće ti se ono što imaš.

437
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:43,160
 Zašto?

438
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,520
 Jer ćeš tada ući,

439
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:47,120
 jer ako si,

440
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:49,840
 ako nemaš onaj drugi život,

441
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:51,320
 onaj drugi svijet,

442
00:28:51,820 --> 00:28:53,260
 ako nemaš duha Božjega,

443
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:53,880
 soli,

444
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,560
 mudrosti križa,

445
00:28:55,560 --> 00:28:57,880
 u tom trenutku te zaokupiraju misli,

446
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,460
 osvete,

447
00:28:58,460 --> 00:29:01,340
 misli kako da uzvratiš zlo na zlo,

448
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:03,820
 znamo kako nam to misli,

449
00:29:03,820 --> 00:29:05,840
 zašto je onaj pustinjak molio,

450
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:08,060
 to je ostalo zapisano za sva vremena,

451
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:11,060
 kad mi dolaze misli srčbe,

452
00:29:11,060 --> 00:29:11,680
