456
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:16,620
 došli su moji krvnici.

457
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:18,240
 Te misli mene kolju,

458
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:20,340
 mene uništavaju život,

459
00:29:20,340 --> 00:29:21,160
 oduzimaju život,

460
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,160
