467
00:29:30,620 --> 00:29:31,880
 to je ono više,

468
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,740
 što svi ljudi hoće,

469
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:35,740
 što svi ljudi traže,

470
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:38,160
 bez čega je nemirno srce naše,

471
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:38,780
 zamisli tada,

472
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:40,220
 možeš ostati u miru,

473
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:42,360
 možeš moliti za tu osobu,

474
00:29:42,760 --> 00:29:43,480
 možeš pustiti,

475
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:45,060
 da ti učini neprav.

476
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:45,700
 Zamisli to,

477
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,140
 zamisli to,

478
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:49,120
 to je onda svječnjak,

479
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:49,740
 to je,

480
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:50,900
 kaže Krist,

481
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,840
 kad govori o fizičkim progonstvima,

482
00:29:52,840 --> 00:29:53,960
 zadesit će vas to,

483
00:29:53,960 --> 00:29:55,060
 radi svjedočenje,

484
00:29:55,060 --> 00:29:56,320
 da se oni spase,

485
00:29:56,320 --> 00:29:58,280
 da do njih dođe sol,

486
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:59,460
 da je njih,

487
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:01,360
 Krist pogleda kroz tvoje,

488
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,720
 zamisli da ti tada imaš oči,

489
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,860
 koje tu osobu ne osuđuju,

490
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:06,160
 nego joj žele dobro.

491
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:06,940
 Eto, to je,

492
00:30:06,940 --> 00:30:08,560
 drugi svijet je u tome,

493
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,800
 blaženstva su u tome,

494
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:10,220
 govor,

495
00:30:10,220 --> 00:30:12,720
 na gori je u tome,

496
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:13,600
 sol je u tome,

497
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,040
 mudrost,

498
00:30:14,040 --> 00:30:14,680
 križa je,

499
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,340
