500
00:30:15,340 --> 00:30:16,640
 i neka niko ne kaže danas,

501
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,880
 ma tu je meni nemoguće.

502
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:18,240
 To je,

503
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,300
 Krist kad je ovo govorio,

504
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:21,320
 govorio to slabim ljudima

505
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,100
 i znao je koliko je to njima nemoguće,

506
00:30:23,100 --> 00:30:24,860
 ali je znao što je to milost,

507
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:26,200
 znao što je to njegov duh.

508
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:31,040
 najnasilniji čovjek može postati blagi čovjek

509
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:32,020
 i postali su mnogi.

510
00:30:32,020 --> 00:30:34,740
 Najbludni čovjek može postati čisti čovjek,

511
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:37,720
 najljeni čovjek može postati revan čovjek,

512
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:39,240
 može imati u sebi revnost

513
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,880
 za svoje spasenje,

514
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,280
 za spasenje drugih oko njega.

515
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:43,700
 Eto, dođe duše sveti,

516
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:46,480
 ne ostavlja nas bezukusne gljutave,

517
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:48,660
 ne ostavlja nas u mraku.

518
00:30:48,660 --> 00:30:51,060
 Daj da može on biti zahvalni

519
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:53,360
 ako nas je dotaklo već ovo svjetlova, sol,

520
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:55,980
 i da ako vidimo da smo u tamih gljutave,

521
00:30:55,980 --> 00:30:56,680
 da tražimo,

522
00:30:56,760 --> 00:31:01,220
 da uđe ovo svjetlova, sol u našoj življi.

523
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:02,140
 Amen.

524
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:31,440
 Dođe duše svjeti,

525
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:35,440
 dođe duše svjeti,

